css
button:focus {
  outline: 2px solid #0066cc;
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* Ensure focus states are visible even if the default outline is removed */
button:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid #0066cc;
}

This snippet ensures buttons have visible focus indicators for keyboard users, improving accessibility without relying on the default (often unstyled) focus outline.
